fields.object_repr: Perfect Cake for the Perfect Wedding Day

fields.title: My little Super Hero!
fields.content:
Thank you so much for the Batman cake for my little Timmy's 8th birthday.
It not only looked perfect, but it tasted great!

fields.title: Perfect Cake for the Perfect Wedding Day
fields.content:
WOW!
The amount of beautiful detail that went into the wedding cake.  It was only out done by the bride!
Outstanding work!  Thank you!

fields.title: It matched his HAT!
fields.content:
The excitement on our little Stevie's face when he saw the cake!
It actually matched his hat and everyone thought it was hilarious!

fields.title: Super Super Girl Cake
fields.content:
Sally loved her Superb Super Girl cake!
And so did we! (when we finally managed to get her to cut it)
She insisted that it was to great to slice up, but when we tasted it....!!
Mmmm lovely!

fields.title: Another Happy Customer
fields.content:
We will definitely be coming back and have given your name to all our friends.

Ace job on our daughter's cake!  Thank you!

fields.description:
The 1-Layer Lilac & Gold Cake is a vision of understated luxury, perfect for intimate wedding celebrations. A flawless ivory base is adorned with a hand-piped lattice of shimmering gold, accented by delicate lilac diamond motifs that draw the eye around the tier. The top is crowned with an artful arrangement of lilac sugar flowers, each petal shaped with care and finished with golden centres that glisten in the light.

Both plant based and gluten free, this cake is as inclusive as it is beautiful, allowing guests to indulge without compromise. With its single elegant tier, it makes a striking yet refined centrepiece — a symbol of love, care, and timeless taste.
fields.name: 1-Layer Lilac & Gold

fields.description:
The 1-Layer Vanilla Roses Cake is a graceful tribute to timeless romance. Its smooth vanilla buttercream, textured in soft, sweeping strokes, forms a delicate canvas for the exquisite floral arrangement. Clusters of sugar roses, daisies, and wild blooms in soft ivory tones are paired with muted foliage, creating an effortlessly natural and romantic look.

With its single, elegant tier, this cake makes an ideal choice for intimate weddings where understated beauty speaks louder than extravagance. The combination of classic flavour and floral artistry ensures every slice is as memorable as the moment it celebrates.
fields.name: 1-Layer Vanilla Roses

fields.description:
The 2-Layer Lilac & Gold Cake offers an elevated take on a classic wedding showpiece. The lower tier is wrapped in an intricate gold lattice, each delicate link resting against a smooth ivory backdrop, while the upper tier remains elegantly simple, tied together by rich lilac satin ribbons.

Crowning the cake is a cascade of handcrafted lilac sugar flowers, each bloom catching the light with subtle golden centres. This combination of regal purple and opulent gold makes for a design that is both sophisticated and memorable — perfect for couples seeking a centrepiece that blends tradition with luxury.

Fully plant based and gluten free, it caters beautifully to a wide range of guests without compromising on taste or style.
fields.name: 2-Layer Lilac & Gold

fields.description:
The 2-Layer Magnolias Cake is a romantic celebration of soft elegance and natural beauty. Each tier is finished in smooth buttercream with gentle, textured strokes, allowing the artistry of the sugar flowers to take centre stage. Large blush-pink magnolias, paired with delicate white blooms and sprigs of greenery, cascade gracefully across the tiers, evoking a fresh, garden-inspired charm.

This design captures the serenity of springtime, making it a perfect choice for weddings where nature’s gentle beauty is part of the celebration. The pairing of classic vanilla tones with lifelike florals creates a centrepiece that is as memorable as it is beautiful.
fields.name: 2-Layer Magnolias

fields.description:
The 2-Layer Summer Fayre Cake is a joyful celebration of vibrant colour and seasonal charm. Each tier is finished with a semi-naked buttercream style and crowned with a cascading white chocolate drip, adding a touch of indulgence to its rustic beauty.

A stunning mix of blooms in deep crimson, soft blush, and delicate pinks is artfully arranged around the tiers, accented by sprigs of berries and tiny white blossoms. This lively arrangement evokes the abundance of a summer garden, making it the perfect centrepiece for weddings filled with warmth, colour, and cheer.
fields.name: 2-Layer Summer Fayre

fields.description:
The 3-Layer Black & Gold Cake is a statement of pure sophistication and drama. Each tier is wrapped in a flawless black fondant canvas, intricately adorned with hand-painted gold lacework and floral detailing. Bold white sugar flowers, accented with gold leaves, provide a striking contrast that draws the eye to every tier.

This cake is the embodiment of luxury, making it a breathtaking centrepiece for couples seeking something unforgettable. Plant based and gluten free, it ensures indulgence for all while maintaining an air of grandeur that is second to none.
fields.name: 3-Layer Black & Gold

fields.description:
The 3-Layer Buttered Pink Cake radiates soft romance with its gentle waves of smooth white buttercream, creating a graceful, flowing texture across each tier. Atop the cake and nestled between the layers, blush-pink sugar roses and delicate sprigs of greenery add a touch of floral charm, while smaller pink accents bring a sweet, whimsical note.

Its timeless design makes it perfect for couples seeking a traditional yet elegant centrepiece. Gluten free for worry-free indulgence, this cake offers a delightful combination of beauty and inclusivity for the wedding table.
fields.name: 3-Layer Buttered Pink

fields.description:
The 3-Layer Dark Fruits Cake is a bold and vibrant showstopper, perfect for couples who want their wedding centrepiece to turn heads. Each tier flows from deep plum to rich magenta in a striking ombré effect, with a textured buttercream finish adding depth and character.

A lavish cascade of handcrafted sugar roses, berries, and blossoms in shades of purple, pink, and violet wraps around the cake, evoking the richness of a summer orchard in full bloom. Every detail bursts with colour and energy, making this a cake that celebrates love in its most passionate form.
fields.name: 3-Layer Dark Fruits

fields.description:
The 3-Layer Lilac & Gold Cake is a regal masterpiece that commands attention. Each tier is adorned with intricate gold patterns, from ornate floral flourishes to delicate lattice detailing, all set against a pristine ivory backdrop. The base tier features rich lilac diamond motifs edged with gold, while a single, elegant lilac bloom crowns the top.

With its harmonious blend of royal purple and shimmering gold, this cake exudes timeless sophistication. Fully plant based and gluten free, it allows every guest to enjoy a slice of luxury without compromise.
fields.name: 3-Layer Lilac & Gold

fields.description:
The 3-Layer Pride Cake bursts with joy, colour, and celebration. Draped in pristine white fondant with flowing ruffle detailing, each tier is brought to life by a vibrant cascade of sugar flowers in the full spectrum of the rainbow — from fiery reds and sunny yellows to cool blues and regal purples.

The bold design celebrates love in all its beautiful diversity, making it a powerful and uplifting wedding centrepiece. Plant based for inclusive indulgence, this cake combines artistry and meaning in every slice.
fields.name: 3-Layer Pride

fields.description:
The 3-Layer Vanilla Chocolate Cake is a rich, indulgent creation designed for chocolate lovers. Each pristine white tier is crowned with a smooth cascade of dark chocolate ganache, dripping elegantly down the sides. Gold leaf accents and handcrafted white sugar roses add a luxurious touch, while scattered chocolate truffles and delicate blooms provide texture and charm.

Perfect for couples who want to combine classic elegance with a decadent twist, this cake is a feast for both the eyes and the palate. Its striking balance of creamy vanilla and deep chocolate tones makes it an unforgettable centrepiece.
fields.name: 3-Layer Vanilla Chocolate

fields.description:
The Buzz Lightyear Cake is a fun-filled treat that’s sure to take celebrations to infinity and beyond. A smooth white fondant base is decorated with colourful stars and a green band, evoking the playful spirit of the beloved space ranger.

Topping the cake is a bold Buzz Lightyear figure, ready for action, making it a perfect choice for fans of the iconic hero. Fully plant based and gluten free, it ensures everyone can join in the fun without missing out on the flavour.
fields.name: Buzz Lightyear

fields.description:
The Hulk Cake smashes its way into any celebration with unstoppable energy. The base is a vivid green fondant tier, streaked with dark drips and surrounded by edible rubble to capture the chaos of Hulk’s arrival.

Emerging from the top is an incredibly detailed 3D Hulk figure, muscles flexed and roaring in classic superhero style. Plant based and gluten free, this cake brings powerful flavour and inclusivity to the table — no one gets left behind in the celebration.
fields.name: Hulk

fields.description:
The Ironman Cake delivers high-tech hero flair to the party table. A deep red fondant base, accented with intricate gold piping, provides the perfect launchpad for a detailed 3D Ironman figure rising from the centre. The glowing arc reactor detail on his chest adds an extra spark of authenticity.

Both plant based and gluten free, this cake ensures every guest can enjoy a taste of superhero action. Ideal for Marvel fans and adventurous celebrations, it’s as bold in flavour as it is in design.
fields.name: Ironman

fields.description:
The Mario-Land Cake is a colourful adventure in edible form. A pastel blue fondant base sets the scene for a lively display of Mario-themed decorations — from cheerful flowers and iconic stars to classic game elements.

Topping the cake are two 3D Mario figures holding balloon-like props, ready to bring the magic of the Mushroom Kingdom to life. Fully plant based and gluten free, this cake is perfect for gamers young and old, ensuring everyone can take part in the fun.
fields.name: Mario-Land

fields.description:
The Spiderman Cake swings straight into the spotlight with bold colours and dynamic detail. A smooth ivory fondant base is accented by a dramatic red drip and Spiderman’s iconic spider emblem. Around the base, edible stones set the urban scene.

Emerging from the top is a striking 3D Spiderman figure in his signature red-and-blue suit, crouched and ready for action. Plant based and gluten free, it ensures everyone at the celebration can enjoy a slice of superhero excitement.
fields.name: Spiderman

fields.description:
The Superman Cake brings heroic grandeur to any celebration. A creamy white fondant base is topped with bold red and blue drips, accented with rocky textures and colourful edible accents.

Kneeling powerfully at the centre is a highly detailed 3D Superman figure, cape billowing and emblem shining — ready to save the day. Plant based for inclusive enjoyment, this cake captures the spirit of the Man of Steel in both design and flavour.
fields.name: Superman

fields.description:
The Wonder-Woman Cake radiates heroic charm and empowerment. Wrapped in bold red and blue fondant with golden accents, the base features Wonder Woman’s iconic emblem surrounded by shining stars.

Perched on top is an adorable chibi-style Wonder Woman figure, complete with her tiara, bracelets, and confident smile — ready to inspire guests of all ages. Plant based and gluten free, it’s a celebration of courage, inclusivity, and deliciousness all in one.
fields.name: Wonder Woman

fields.description:
The Woody Cake captures the heart and charm of the beloved Toy Story sheriff. The base, in warm caramel tones with playful red piping, evokes a cheerful western theme that perfectly complements the character.

On top sits a detailed Woody figure, complete with cowboy hat, sheriff’s badge, and friendly wave — ready to bring a little “Howdy, partner!” to the celebration. Plant based and gluten free, it’s a cake that invites everyone to join the fun.
fields.name: Woody

fields.description:
The Batman Cake delivers dark, brooding elegance with a heroic edge. The base, in deep charcoal fondant, is accented with golden Gotham-inspired silhouettes and the iconic bat symbol.

Rising from the centre is a striking 3D Batman figure, sculpted with powerful detail and surrounded by a dramatic cape effect. Perfect for fans of the Dark Knight, this cake is a bold centrepiece that blends artistry and strength.
fields.name: Batman

fields.description:
The Confetti Cake is a joyful burst of colour and sweetness. A smooth pink-and-white buttercream base is topped with a generous swirl of icing, cascading in playful drips down the sides.

A shower of rainbow sprinkles crowns the cake, adding crunch, colour, and pure party vibes. Plant based and gluten free, it’s a cheerful treat that everyone can enjoy — perfect for birthdays, milestones, or any moment worth celebrating.
fields.name: Confetti

fields.description:
The Fun-Fayre Cake is a carnival of colour and excitement. A smooth white icing base is decorated with playful drips, a cascade of rainbow sprinkles, and swirls of piped frosting topped with bright chocolate balls.

Three whimsical cone-shaped toppers crown the cake, bringing a touch of fairground fun to the table. Plant based for wide enjoyment, this cake is a vibrant choice for birthdays, parties, and any celebration that calls for a little extra cheer.
fields.name: Fun-Fayre

fields.description:
The Blue-Ice Cake is a frosty vision of elegance, perfect for winter-themed celebrations. Soft blue buttercream wraps the cake, adorned with swirls of white and icy blue frosting. Edible pearls and delicate sugar decorations give the effect of shimmering snow and frost.

Its cool colour palette and intricate piping make it a showstopper for birthdays, anniversaries, or any event that calls for a touch of frozen beauty. Gluten free for inclusive indulgence, it’s as beautiful as it is delicious.
fields.name: Blue-Ice

fields.description:
The Rainbow-Melt Cake is a joyful explosion of colour and fun. Wrapped in vibrant rainbow buttercream, it features bright orange and purple drips that cascade playfully down the sides. A crown of rainbow swirls, topped with a scattering of sprinkles, adds a festive finishing touch.

Perfect for birthdays, pride events, or any celebration that calls for pure happiness, this cake is both plant based and gluten free — making sure everyone can enjoy the party.
fields.name: Rainbow Melt

fields.description:
The Pride-Swirl Cake is a vibrant celebration of colour and inclusivity. Smooth white fondant sets the stage for bold swirls of rainbow-coloured frosting that wrap around the cake like a joyful ribbon. The top is crowned with more rainbow swirls, sprinkled with a touch of sparkle.

Perfect for pride events, birthdays, or any occasion that calls for a burst of happiness, this cake is plant based to ensure more guests can enjoy its beauty and flavour.
fields.name: Pride Swirl

fields.description: The Floral Cake is a garden in full bloom, captured in sugar artistry. A pristine white fondant base provides the perfect backdrop for a cascade of vibrant, hand-crafted flowers in pinks, purples, blues, and yellows, each petal shaped with care. This cheerful and elegant design brings a burst of colour to any event, from birthdays to afternoon tea celebrations. Plant based and gluten free, it’s a treat that blends beauty, inclusivity, and flavour in every slice.
fields.name: Wall Flowers
